channel.description: Recent content on Alex Paynter's site

item.description: Alex Paynter is a statistician (data scientist, if you prefer). Since 2023 he has worked for Sage Bionetworks, mostly on AACR’s Project GENIE. From 2019 to 2023 he worked with a group in Seattle Children’s Hospital coordination national studies of cystic fibrosis. This website is a place for personal projects and stray thoughts. Welcome and enjoy your stay.
